name: MORNING HQ
address: 240 MacPherson Rd, #02-02 Pines Industrial Building, Singapore 348574
author: Vidin Andonov
review_text:
Best capsule machine on the market and a huge variety of specialty coffee capsules all in one place! What else could a man ask for?
Oh yeah - and a cool Mobile App to control the machine, brew the roasters recipes and do in-app purchases
